'''Mario Masla<U+0107>''' ([[Serbian Cyrillic alphabet|Serbian Cyrillic]]: Map<U+0438>o Mac<U+043B>a<U+045B>, born 9 September 1990 in [[Novi Sad]]) is a [[Serbia]]n [[Association football|football]] [[Defender (association football)|defender]] playing with [[FK Borac <U+010C>a<U+010D>ak]] in the [[Serbian SuperLiga]].

He made his senior debut in the season 2008-09 with [[FK Veternik]] before moving in summer 2009 to [[FK Borac <U+010C>a<U+010D>ak]].<ref>[http://www.srbijafudbal.net/borac/maslac.htm Mario Masla<U+0107>] at Srbijafudbal</ref> He plays as central defender.

He is member of the [[Serbia national under-21 football team]].<ref>[http://www.transfermarkt.co.uk/en/mario-maslac/profil/spieler_75808.html Mario Masla<U+0107>] at Transfermarkt</ref>

